Rub rim of martini glass (about 1-cup size) with a lime wedge. Pour red sugar into a saucer. Dip damp glass rims into sugar to coat. Chill glasses. Mix together rum, lime juice, limoncello, and simple syrup; keep cold. Mound equal portions raspberry slush into prepared glasses. Pour equal portions rum mixture over slush. Use a straw to blend the cooler and sip.